    "description": "While equipped, it regenerates SMG ammo. Reloading tosses a bouncing unit that sprays shots in all directions, then detonates. The roaming bullets benefit strongly from gun damage and amp effects. The final explosion also scales with leftover magazine rounds, and the fuse becomes shorter when your SMG reserves are low."
